{"tid":535973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女子曲棍隊亞運外圍賽 港隊摘銀贏入場券","createTime":"2018-01-21T11:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-21T12:03:46.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"073f6d025def2a13c44451595f5b1a3bd2ec969f","tid":535973,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T11:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/195846_949c269a568d46bdbd7871a0c292c366.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F195846_949c269a568d46bdbd7871a0c292c366.png&h=16ee20c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【體路專訊】2018年亞運會女子曲棍球外圍賽於本月12至20日假泰國舉行，香港娘子軍表現出色，經過6場賽事後憑較佳得失球力壓中華台北勇奪銀牌，順利贏得雅加達亞運會入場券。<br />\n<br />\n今次外圍賽共有7支隊伍參賽，以單循環形式進行，成績最好的4隊可獲亞運會資格，港隊在6場賽事中取得3場勝仗，分別以3：0擊敗印尼、哈薩克，4：0橫掃巴基斯坦，另以1：1及0：0戰平對新加坡及中華台北，面對勁旅泰國亦僅以0：1告負。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最終泰國以5勝1負得15分封后，港隊以3勝2和1負與中華台北同獲11分，但憑較佳得失球名列亞軍，寶島屈居季軍，哈薩克排第4。這是香港女曲第3度入圍亞運會，同時首次在外圍賽中染指獎牌。<br />\n<br />\n2018年亞運會將於8月18至9月2日在印尼雅加達舉行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sportsroad.hk/archives/186622\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsportsroad.hk%2Farchives%2F186622&d=AmyvZJfVCLEFjrm7gTaWZbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=8c0d0c00\" target=\"_blank\">https://sportsroad.hk/archives/186622</a>"},{"pid":"506b849de32009652bda821697724fecba882391","tid":535973,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T12:00:07.000Z","msg":"求高清"},{"pid":"c9cbd3d1f7662d4843922e02de7ae4453d93254b","tid":535973,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"506b849de32009652bda821697724fecba882391","tid":535973,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T12:00:07.000Z","msg":"求高清"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T12:02:11.000Z","msg":"前排左二ok"},{"pid":"29a6cafa79621cd1e67a81fa83977fbb6d05b10d","tid":535973,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9cbd3d1f7662d4843922e02de7ae4453d932